if {WinnieSucksAss} == true:
	[signal arg="marlonSittin"]
	[voice path="res://sounds/actThreeDialogue/WinnieDidBad/Marlton/wow.mp3" volume="0.0"]
	MarlonRedWood: Wow.
	[voice path="res://sounds/actThreeDialogue/WinnieDidBad/Marlton/goinghome.mp3" volume="0.0"]
	MarlonRedWood: I am going home.
	[signal arg="marlonWalkingAway"]
	[voice path="res://sounds/actThreeDialogue/WinnieDidBad/Winnie/waitadamnminute.mp3" volume="0.0"]
	WinnieCLester: S-Shut up! Wait! Wait a damn minute!
	[signal arg="marlonSmirk"]
	[voice path="res://sounds/actThreeDialogue/WinnieDidBad/Marlton/BetterBeGood.mp3" volume="0.0"]
	MarlonRedWood: Better be good, you’ve already wasted enough of my time.
	[voice path="res://sounds/actThreeDialogue/WinnieDidBad/Winnie/HuntingMatch.mp3" volume="0.0"]
	WinnieCLester: How about a hunting match. One on One! Five rounds, no turns, whoever hunts down the most birds wins!
	[signal arg="marlonLooksDown"]
	MarlonRedWood: ...
	[signal arg="marlonSighs"]
	[voice path="res://sounds/actThreeDialogue/WinnieDidBad/Marlton/WhateverYouSay.mp3" volume="0.0"]
	MarlonRedWood: Whatever you say, Winnie. I got nothing better to do with my life anyway.
else:
	[signal arg="marlonImpressed"]
	[voice path="res://sounds/actThreeDialogue/WinnieDidGood/Marlton/RevolverOcelot.mp3" volume="0.0"]
	MarlonRedWood: That was some fancy shooting. You’re pretty good, Winnie. Bu-
	[signal arg="winnieSmile"]
	[voice path="res://sounds/actThreeDialogue/WinnieDidGood/Winnie/EgoForNothing.mp3" volume="0.0"]
	WinnieCLester: Do you think this ego was for nothing?
	[voice path="res://sounds/actThreeDialogue/WinnieDidGood/Marlton/ButItsNotEnough.mp3" volume="0.0"]
	MarlonRedWood: But it’s not enough.
	[voice path="res://sounds/actThreeDialogue/WinnieDidGood/Winnie/Showcaseofpower.mp3" volume="0.0"]
	WinnieCLester: What...? Need more of a showcase of my power?
	[signal arg="marlonStandUp"]
	[voice path="res://sounds/actThreeDialogue/WinnieDidGood/Marlton/ToProveYourself.mp3" volume="0.0"]
	MarlonRedWood: To prove yourself, how about having a hunting match. The rules are-
	[voice path="res://sounds/actThreeDialogue/WinnieDidGood/Winnie/shootsDownBirdsWins.mp3" volume="0.0"]
	WinnieCLester: Let me guess... Five rounds, whoever shoots down the most birds wins?
	[voice path="res://sounds/actThreeDialogue/WinnieDidGood/Marlton/PrettySharp.mp3" volume="0.0"]
	MarlonRedWood: Pretty sharp, youngster.
	[voice path="res://sounds/actThreeDialogue/WinnieDidGood/Winnie/withoutmywit.mp3" volume="0.0"]
	WinnieCLester: Wouldn’t be here today without my wit.